Interface UploadCompletionBlock


  • public interface UploadCompletionBlock
    This interface is for the callback used when the file has finished uploading.

      void callback(MoBackFile file, MoBackStatus status)

    • Method Detail

      • callback

        void callback(MoBackFile file,
            MoBackStatus status)
        This callback is used when the uploading of a file is finished.
        Parameters:
        file - The MoBackFile data object of the file that was uploaded. This is what you will put as the value of your MoBackFile variable in your custom MoBackObject, so that you save a reference to the file.
        status - The status of the upload task.
